  "detailed_description": "<strong>Features in Early Access</strong><br><br><strong>◆ SWORD & SPELLS</strong><br>You can attack enemies with a greatsword to restore mana and gain an advantage in combat by using spells.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233820/extras/4508f6481bce71f2f0b54e9684d3fa64.avif?t=1714912635\" width=640 height=256 /></span><br><br><strong>◆ ARMORS</strong><br>Achieve challenges to unlock various distinctive equipment.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233820/extras/a2ec383b181ec3c15085f5c96dce2cbf.avif?t=1714912635\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><strong>◆ ITEMS</strong><br>Collect gold coins and buy items that can lead the combat to your advantage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233820/extras/a7e3ec8632bd52bca6e43c59fcb8a967.avif?t=1714912635\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><strong>◆ BOSSES</strong><br>Survive until the end and confront the final enemy.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233820/extras/87b320768bea9ff80751c2bd761f4287.avif?t=1714912635\" width=640 height=360 /></span>",
